Carl A. SCHUG, Trustee in Bankruptcy of WINNER-FRANCK BAKING COMPANY, Appellant, v. Norman S. CALDWELL, Joseph W. Franck, et al., Appellees. No. 4928. Circuit Court of Appeals, Third Circuit. Nov. 29, 1932. A. R. Jackson, of Williamsport, Pa., for appellant. John E. Cupp and Mortimer C. Rhone, both of Williamsport, Pa., for appellees.

Before WOOLLEY, DAVIS, and THOMPSON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed on Judge Johnson’s opinion [58 F.(2d) 409].
